  ;; ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
  ;; U6 - RT9193-33GB  3.3V 300mA LDO  SOT-23-5
  ;; [FIX v1.1] Replaced TLV75533PDBVR (200mV Vdrop) with RT9193-33GB (150mV Vdrop)
  ;; Vdrop at 300mA: 150mV → holds 3.3V until VBAT drops to ~3.45V
  ;; TLV75533 would drop out at VBAT=3.5V → Brownout at low battery
  ;; Pin-compatible with TLV75533 (SOT-23-5, same pinout)
  ;; ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
